AMPDISCOVERYSERVICE(8) System Manager's Manual AMPDISCOVERYSERVICE(8)

NAME

AMPDiscoveryService — The discovery service for managing iOS/iPod device discovery

SYNOPSIS

AMPDiscoveryService

DESCRIPTION

AMPDiscoveryService is a per-user daemon which discovers attached iOS/iPod devices.

There are no configuration options to AMPDiscoveryService. Users should not run AMPDiscoveryService it manually.
